  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3305590/" class="title-link">易中天拿出干货了</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3305590"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/elact/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1123727-6.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/elact/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Elact</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-06-01"
      class="main-meta">2010-06-01 14:00:41</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3305590_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  先说个问题，排版有点乱，文章以问答的形式出现，用空白小方格和黑色小方格代表问答双方，阅读起来不习惯。  和《品三国》之类作者的其他书比，《我山之石》无论是从层次还是见解上都高出一筹。  内容很强，解释了儒、道、墨、法四家（顺道说了说“一毛不拔”杨朱的思想）对于...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3305590/#comments">(7回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">6有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3305590_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3305590_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2228184">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2228184/" class="title-link">易中天老师最好的一部作品</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2228184"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/3588821/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3588821/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">发现者</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-08-14"
      class="main-meta">2009-08-14 17:51:15</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2228184_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  在易老师已经出版的书中，我首推这部《我山之石》。    其次是《帝国的终结》，不是《帝国的惆怅》。  第三是《美国宪法的诞生和我们的反思》。  第四是《先秦诸子百家争鸣》。    而我目前正在看《成都方式》。    《我山之石》可以说是写的最流畅的一本，几乎是只花了不到一...

